Orchestra nodded.

"Yes, I came here for peace talks.  We Predacons, under Darkfate's command,
would like to establish an alliance with you, say, cease fire and shared
information," Orchestra said.

Composer replied.

"Alright, I'll be right there," Composer said, then started off to the
conference room.
